reviews.review_text:
NICE Another fantastic Uptown show.  
The quality of the recording is stellar.  Yeah, there are some equipment issues etc., but this is as good as it gets.  You will rarely find fidelity like this during this era.  I am going to attribute it largely to the lack of NR in the recording.  Lap it up!
Uptown 81' This is a nice Chi-town show.Decent first set with a much better second set.
